rows.name: Ask Zo Geil about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066901_MSG0001
rows.name:
Amongst our house is a young woman named Zazhi.
How stubborn she is![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066901_MSG0002
rows.name:
Now that she is of age, I have tried to find her a
respectable house to marry into.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066901_MSG0003
rows.name:
But her quest for vengeance causes her to forget her
manners. She wore ARMOR to the last matchmaking
ceremony in lieu of proper attire! Pah![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066901_MSG0004
rows.name:
Will Zazhi wear armor to her wedding as well?
Will she fight? This is the sort of gossip she invites.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066901_MSG0009
rows.name:
I have sent a soldier of mine, Gu Ladha, to your city.
But it sounds as though she is struggling and has
no one to turn to.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066901_MSG0010
rows.name:
A man's troubles can be wrested away by good friends
and strong drink.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066901_MSG0011
rows.name: But Ladha is a woman. How do I talk to her?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066901_MSG0012
rows.name: I hope she finds some lass she can confide in.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066901_MSG0013
rows.name:
But knowing her, she will push away any who try to
get close to her. That one likes her solitary gloom.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066901_MSG0018
rows.name:
Since making Gu Ladha liaison, our deliberations with
humans have proceeded much more smoothly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066901_MSG0019
rows.name:
Her attentive personality works in our favor here.
I appreciate your sage advice.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066901_MSG0020
rows.name:
Like most Wrothians, I have a habit of placing battle
prowess above all else.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066901_MSG0021
rows.name:
But if we are to live in this city, we must avail ourselves
of ALL our strengths.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066901_MSG0022
rows.name:
You have taught me that a leader like myself needs to
be able to spot these gifts amongst his soldiers.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066901_MSG0027
rows.name:
Until recently, a soldier of mine, Gu Ladha,
was all wound up in her problems.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066901_MSG0028
rows.name:
But something has snapped her out of her gloom,
and now she throws herself at her training with
abandon. I marvel at the progress she has made.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066901_MSG0029
rows.name:
She always showed a gift for Skells. If she keeps it up,
she shall do great things on the battlefield when we
face off against the Ganglion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev066901_MSG0030
rows.name:
I wish I knew who put her back on such a positive
path so I could thank them myself.[ST:wait ]
